picam-raw (1.0.0+202606041025-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial release. Replaced RTSP/H.264 pipeline with raw YUV420 UDP streaming.
  * Dual streams: main (2304x1296) on :8560, lores (640x360) on :8561.
  * Client registration via UDP datagram; 30-second FPS console logging.

